      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "APPELLANT (2) was well in the market last time but only managed fifth (23.71), beaten 8 lengths. Finished second the start before. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Tough to beat if on-song. AROUND OUTSIDE (1) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind COSTLY HABITS (17.88) in a Grade 6/MDN. Has the pace to be prominent. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Winning chance. COSTLY HABITS (8) has some solid form under his belt and proved too classy last time to win by 2 lengths at this track in a handy 17.74 beating AROUND OUTSIDE. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from four starts. Makes plenty of appeal if runs up to latest. ADHANA MARTINA (7) is among the chances again if she runs up to the latest effort.",
